title: War of the Roses: The Receipt with Roller Dogs on It
description: Sam is wondering if his girlfriend Zoey is cheating with a guy in a band she always likes to go see.  They haven't been having sex AND he found a receipt for 3 roller dogs in the garage and she wouldn't eat that many roller dogs on her own!
